channel.title: Short tracks with TF2 voices [song list]
channel.description:
I made some short tracks with Team Fortress 2 character quotes and posted on Instagram. All of them are quite short (because those are made for insta post), and I think it’s too short to advertise separately, so I made this list. Hope you enjoy the feeling of good old days of TF2 memes.
“Giddy up!”[Bounce] & “Medic’s favorite” [Bounce] https://instagram.com/p/BkM4btFAcgP/ “Happy dynamite”[Chill house] https://instagram.com/p/BkQBXbJgqbJ/ “Miss you rain” [Deep house] https://instagram.com/p/Bkm8ReQAF1j/
